name: Exclusive Series Capa FF (NHC)
additionalNotes:
From NHC

These bundles of 25 production sticks were pulled out in Esteli for being 'a size too large'.  Normally 5 5/8 x 46 (hint, hint), these are more like 47-48.  Using new molds that may have been a bit too big, the factory created 50 groups of 25 sticks that were identified in the drying room as being a bit off in size.
